COWBAT Documentation


CFIA OLC Workflow for Bacterial Assembly and Typing




Commands




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.
